00:26:25,940 --> 00:26:26,980
[SPEAKER_01] o molitvi,

791
00:26:26,980 --> 00:26:28,380
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam tumačio o čenaš,

792
00:26:28,380 --> 00:26:29,599
[SPEAKER_01] tako je ogromni ciklusi,

793
00:26:29,599 --> 00:26:31,359
[SPEAKER_01] no ovo zanima svijet.

794
00:26:31,359 --> 00:26:32,759
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo svijet, tako je.

795
00:26:32,759 --> 00:26:33,740
[SPEAKER_01] Oni skoče na to,

796
00:26:33,740 --> 00:26:33,900
[SPEAKER_01] jel?

797
00:26:35,180 --> 00:26:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] i naravno,

798
00:26:35,960 --> 00:26:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] osluškujem ljude.

799
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:40,240
[SPEAKER_01] I ja da sam možda više slušao studente,

800
00:26:40,240 --> 00:26:41,279
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam uvijek ankete,

801
00:26:41,279 --> 00:26:43,099
[SPEAKER_01] oni su uvijek tražili temu o spolnosti.

802
00:26:43,099 --> 00:26:43,519
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek.

803
00:26:43,519 --> 00:26:47,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja sam znao da moram im dati ne toliko što žele,

804
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:49,099
[SPEAKER_01] nego što moraju čuti.

805
00:26:49,259 --> 00:26:50,519
[SPEAKER_01] pa sam dao ispolnost,

806
00:26:50,519 --> 00:26:51,099
[SPEAKER_01] ali sam dao,

807
00:26:51,099 --> 00:26:53,740
[SPEAKER_01] tako ja sam smatrao u jednom trenutku ono i moraju znaći šta je ehoristija.

808
00:26:53,740 --> 00:26:58,259
[SPEAKER_01] Pa sam imao ogroman jedan ciklus od 12 predavanje o sakramentima ehoristiji.

809
00:26:58,940 --> 00:27:02,299
[SPEAKER_01] I je, možda malo manje brojka padne,

810
00:27:02,299 --> 00:27:05,480
[SPEAKER_01] ali su brojke bili ogromne,

811
00:27:05,480 --> 00:27:07,400
[SPEAKER_01] ali jest, ovo su bombastične teme,

812
00:27:07,400 --> 00:27:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] koje svakoga,

813
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:09,299
[SPEAKER_01] to je tako intimno,

814
00:27:09,299 --> 00:27:10,819
[SPEAKER_01] to tako pogađa svakog čovjeka,

815
00:27:10,819 --> 00:27:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali treba integralno o svemu pričati.

816
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:15,519
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, ali u konečnici ovo što si rekao,

817
00:27:15,519 --> 00:27:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] ako čovjek ne razumije,

818
00:27:18,440 --> 00:27:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] a onda i ne osjeća ehoristiju,

819
00:27:20,519 --> 00:27:24,480
[SPEAKER_00] onda u stvari provedba svega onoga druga što razgovaramo,

820
00:27:24,480 --> 00:27:25,220
[SPEAKER_00] teško moži.

821
00:27:25,220 --> 00:27:27,299
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da spolnost je samo jedan postotak toga svega.

822
00:27:27,299 --> 00:27:34,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ali jedna tema koja je i danas često aktualna među mladima

823
00:27:34,279 --> 00:27:37,180
[SPEAKER_00] je taj život, zajednički život prije braka.

824
00:27:37,180 --> 00:27:37,839
[SPEAKER_01] Kohabitacija.

825
00:27:37,839 --> 00:27:38,799
[SPEAKER_00] Kohabitacija, tako.

826
00:27:38,799 --> 00:27:42,940
[SPEAKER_00] I to je jedna, imam dojam da u stvari tu sad postoji

827
00:27:42,940 --> 00:27:47,500
[SPEAKER_00] da je došlo do jednog ulaza različitih pogrišnih tumačenja,

828
00:27:47,500 --> 00:27:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] važnosti, važnosti toga da mladi ljudi

829
00:27:50,900 --> 00:27:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] kroz ženitbeni sakrament,

830
00:27:52,380 --> 00:27:54,519
[SPEAKER_00] oni koji su vijernici kroz ženitbeni sakrament,

831
00:27:54,519 --> 00:27:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] počnemo zajedno živjeti, a ne prije.

832
00:27:56,819 --> 00:28:00,539
[SPEAKER_00] A neko ko kao da je to bez veze kao, pa to je samo forma.

833
00:28:00,539 --> 00:28:01,400
[SPEAKER_01] Je, ovako.

834
00:28:01,400 --> 00:28:04,240
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam isto tu doživio jednu evoluciju.

835
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:05,880
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam postao svečenik,

836
00:28:05,880 --> 00:28:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] ja apsolutno nisam tu temu dirao.

837
00:28:08,960 --> 00:28:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

838
00:28:09,960 --> 00:28:13,380
[SPEAKER_01] ja nisam kao mladi svečenik imao argument.

839
00:28:13,380 --> 00:28:14,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ako dvoje mladi se vole,

840
00:28:14,599 --> 00:28:16,380
[SPEAKER_01] žene se za šest mjeseci,

841
00:28:17,799 --> 00:28:21,519
[SPEAKER_01] bolje sad saznat i bolje se upoznat nego kasnije,

842
00:28:21,519 --> 00:28:23,460
[SPEAKER_01] pa ajmo živit zajedno,

843
00:28:23,460 --> 00:28:24,460
[SPEAKER_01] jer to je ta logika.

844
00:28:24,460 --> 00:28:26,480
[SPEAKER_01] Što je dobra namjerna zapravo.

845
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:27,559
[SPEAKER_01] Da je, pa naravno.

846
00:28:27,559 --> 00:28:28,640
[SPEAKER_01] Da neko od toga,

847
00:28:28,640 --> 00:28:31,579
[SPEAKER_01] da ja upirem prstu nekoga,

848
00:28:31,579 --> 00:28:33,519
[SPEAKER_01] stvarno ti mladi imaju dobru namjeru,

849
00:28:33,519 --> 00:28:34,079
[SPEAKER_01] kao, hej,

850
00:28:34,079 --> 00:28:35,420
[SPEAKER_01] idemo sad živit zajedno,

851
00:28:35,420 --> 00:28:37,279
[SPEAKER_01] šest, sedem mjeseci, godno dana prije.

852
00:28:37,279 --> 00:28:38,839
[SPEAKER_00] I zašto bi plaćali dva stana?

853
00:28:38,839 --> 00:28:39,740
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraj krajeva i to.

854
00:28:39,740 --> 00:28:40,779
[SPEAKER_00] To je tako vidjeno ono, da.

855
00:28:40,779 --> 00:28:41,940
[SPEAKER_01] I idemo vidjeti,

856
00:28:41,940 --> 00:28:42,660
[SPEAKER_01] jes voli mi zato,

857
00:28:42,660 --> 00:28:45,099
[SPEAKER_01] jer ne želimo kasnije doći do razvoda.

858
00:28:45,099 --> 00:28:47,500
[SPEAKER_01] I to je stvarno dobro namjerno

859
00:28:47,500 --> 00:28:49,319
[SPEAKER_01] i ja sam to prošutio.

860
00:28:49,319 --> 00:28:50,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam to vidio,

861
00:28:50,460 --> 00:28:51,319
[SPEAKER_01] kao mladi kapelan.

862
00:28:51,319 --> 00:28:53,279
[SPEAKER_01] No, šta sam od nam primijetio?

863
00:28:53,279 --> 00:28:56,359
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan, nakon par godina svečenstva

864
00:28:56,359 --> 00:28:57,839
[SPEAKER_01] dolaze ljudi,

865
00:28:57,839 --> 00:28:58,799
[SPEAKER_01] nakon dvi, tri, četiri,

866
00:28:58,799 --> 00:29:00,519
[SPEAKER_01] pješ, šest, sedam, deset godina braka

867
00:29:00,519 --> 00:29:01,400
[SPEAKER_01] i razvod.

868
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:03,920
[SPEAKER_01] A najproblematičnije je bilo

869
00:29:03,920 --> 00:29:05,359
[SPEAKER_01] kad neko dođe nakon godinu dana

870
00:29:05,359 --> 00:29:07,539
[SPEAKER_01] i malo i kreneš proces s njima.

871
00:29:07,539 --> 00:29:09,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pričaš i s njom, i s njim.

872
00:29:09,539 --> 00:29:11,740
[SPEAKER_01] Pokušavaš sanirat, ne ide,

873
00:29:11,740 --> 00:29:13,200
[SPEAKER_01] pa traže crkveno poništenje,

874
00:29:13,200 --> 00:29:14,619
[SPEAKER_01] pa dođeš do ti nužni pitanja,

875
00:29:14,619 --> 00:29:15,240
[SPEAKER_01] kako su živjeli.

876
00:29:15,240 --> 00:29:16,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam primijetio nešto,

877
00:29:16,940 --> 00:29:19,319
[SPEAKER_01] da baš oni koji su živjeli

878
00:29:19,319 --> 00:29:20,519
[SPEAKER_01] zajedno prije braka,

879
00:29:20,519 --> 00:29:21,819
[SPEAKER_01] završavaju razvod.

880
00:29:21,819 --> 00:29:23,720
[SPEAKER_01] To je meni bilo, kako se kaže,

881
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:24,640
[SPEAKER_01] nesam wake up call.

882
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:26,559
[SPEAKER_00] Poziv na buđenje.

883
00:29:26,559 --> 00:29:27,180
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je ovo?

884
00:29:27,180 --> 00:29:28,819
[SPEAKER_01] Kako je ovo sad moguće?

885
00:29:29,779 --> 00:29:31,420
[SPEAKER_01] A suprato, tome sam vidio parove

886
00:29:31,420 --> 00:29:33,559
[SPEAKER_01] koji tak nisu živjeli.

887
00:29:33,559 --> 00:29:35,539
[SPEAKER_01] Koji su živjeli ono što crkva govori,

888
00:29:35,539 --> 00:29:36,720
[SPEAKER_01] učistoći, odvojeno.

889
00:29:36,720 --> 00:29:38,839
[SPEAKER_01] I oni ostaju u braku.

890
00:29:38,839 --> 00:29:40,240
[SPEAKER_01] Sada, jedan disklejmer.

891
00:29:40,240 --> 00:29:42,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne govorim, niti tvrdim,

892
00:29:42,500 --> 00:29:44,460
[SPEAKER_01] da svatko koji živi zajedno prije braka

893
00:29:44,460 --> 00:29:45,500
[SPEAKER_01] će završiti u razvod.

894
00:29:45,500 --> 00:29:47,359
[SPEAKER_01] Niti svatko koji živi u čistoći.

895
00:29:47,359 --> 00:29:50,460
[SPEAKER_00] Da će ostati u lijepom i sretnom braku

896
00:29:50,460 --> 00:29:51,799
[SPEAKER_00] do kraja života, naravno.

897
00:29:51,799 --> 00:29:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali govoriš o svom iskustvu.

898
00:29:53,619 --> 00:29:55,299
[SPEAKER_00] Svom ograničenom iskustvu.

899
00:29:55,299 --> 00:29:57,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ja govorim o mom iskustvu 21 godina svećenja

900
00:29:57,960 --> 00:29:59,400
[SPEAKER_01] koja mene ne može tu niko pobijati

901
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:00,660
[SPEAKER_01] zato što sam to doživio.

902
00:30:00,660 --> 00:30:03,680
[SPEAKER_00] I koja je u konačnici tebe potaknula

903
00:30:03,680 --> 00:30:06,559
[SPEAKER_00] da preispitaš na što treba štavljati naglasa.

904
00:30:06,559 --> 00:30:07,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ondan sam ja u svećeničem kruvi.

905
00:30:07,960 --> 00:30:09,339
[SPEAKER_01] Ej, dečki, ste vi ovo primijetili?

906
00:30:09,339 --> 00:30:10,500
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto mi šutim ovo me?

907
00:30:10,500 --> 00:30:13,400
[SPEAKER_01] E, ali šta je?

908
00:30:13,400 --> 00:30:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] Oprostite da te prigem.

909
00:30:14,460 --> 00:30:19,180
[SPEAKER_00] Poanta za jedan dobar dio ljudi

910
00:30:19,180 --> 00:30:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] koji ovo što si rekao mladih

911
00:30:20,500 --> 00:30:22,299
[SPEAKER_00] koji idu živjeti zajedno prije nego s išto.

912
00:30:22,299 --> 00:30:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Poanta je u probi.

913
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] To je kao brak na probu.

914
00:30:25,420 --> 00:30:27,140
[SPEAKER_00] Da mi vidimo da li si mi pašemo.

915
00:30:27,140 --> 00:30:29,539
[SPEAKER_00] I onda oni kao obave probu

916
00:30:29,539 --> 00:30:31,400
[SPEAKER_00] a onda se pokaže da ta proba nije...

917
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,220
[SPEAKER_00] I doći ja do toga.

918
00:30:32,220 --> 00:30:33,400
[SPEAKER_01] Nego šta je se dogodilo?

919
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:35,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam vidio da

920
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:37,920
[SPEAKER_01] nakon sedam meseci

921
00:30:37,920 --> 00:30:40,279
[SPEAKER_01] godinu dana braka, razvod

922
00:30:40,279 --> 00:30:42,319
[SPEAKER_01] i čak sam primijetio

923
00:30:42,319 --> 00:30:44,319
[SPEAKER_01] korelaciju što su više živjeli zajedno.

924
00:30:44,420 --> 00:30:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] četiri, pet, šest, sedam godina

925
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:49,480
[SPEAKER_01] nakon pet, šest, sedam meseci braka, razvod.

926
00:30:49,480 --> 00:30:50,759
[SPEAKER_01] Ja tako šta je ovo?

927
00:30:50,759 --> 00:30:53,440
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, upravo se događa ono

928
00:30:53,440 --> 00:30:54,599
[SPEAKER_01] što su htjeli spriječiti

929
00:30:54,599 --> 00:30:57,400
[SPEAKER_01] s ovim i jedan par, pa drugi par,

930
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:58,759
[SPEAKER_01] pa treći par, pa četvrti par.

931
00:30:58,759 --> 00:31:00,759
[SPEAKER_01] I onda sam dobio hladan tuš

932
00:31:00,759 --> 00:31:03,460
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam bio prije Vašingtona

933
00:31:03,460 --> 00:31:04,779
[SPEAKER_01] prije da sam išao na ime.

934
00:31:04,779 --> 00:31:06,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam posao Sočini dvije druge

935
00:31:06,119 --> 00:31:08,180
[SPEAKER_01] išao sam na studij dvije sedmene.

936
00:31:08,180 --> 00:31:09,339
[SPEAKER_01] I šta je se dogodilo?

937
00:31:09,339 --> 00:31:11,279
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je bilo providonosno.

938
00:31:11,900 --> 00:31:13,279
[SPEAKER_01] Ako se sjećate, Luke Rađe.

939
00:31:13,279 --> 00:31:14,039
[SPEAKER_00] Da, sjećam.

940
00:31:14,039 --> 00:31:15,140
[SPEAKER_01] Koji je nastradao, nažalost.

941
00:31:15,140 --> 00:31:16,119
[SPEAKER_00] Da, prometnoj nesredi.

942
00:31:16,119 --> 00:31:16,900
[SPEAKER_01] Tad je on bio

943
00:31:16,900 --> 00:31:19,759
[SPEAKER_01] glavna faca svećeniku Zagrebi.

944
00:31:19,759 --> 00:31:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] Je, je upalno su ćeo Isusovac.

945
00:31:21,960 --> 00:31:23,160
[SPEAKER_01] On je bio, ono,

946
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:24,859
[SPEAKER_01] Luka je bio svima nama

947
00:31:24,859 --> 00:31:26,359
[SPEAKER_01] mladim svećenicima neki ideal.

948
00:31:26,359 --> 00:31:28,200
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam znao kao mladim svećenici

949
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:28,859
[SPEAKER_01] i njega slušati.

950
00:31:28,859 --> 00:31:31,900
[SPEAKER_01] I on je na strado.

951
00:31:31,900 --> 00:31:33,819
[SPEAKER_00] Završio u kolicima.

952
00:31:33,819 --> 00:31:34,240
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

953
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:35,660
[SPEAKER_01] I onda, ajde,

954
00:31:35,660 --> 00:31:37,440
[SPEAKER_01] kako su došli do mene,

955
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:39,079
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam tek bio mladim kapelan

956
00:31:39,079 --> 00:31:41,519
[SPEAKER_01] da ja dođem i malo o tome pričam.

957
00:31:41,519 --> 00:31:43,779
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, ja sam već znao za teologiju tijela,

958
00:31:43,779 --> 00:31:45,839
[SPEAKER_01] ali nisam znao detalje sve.

959
00:31:45,839 --> 00:31:48,940
[SPEAKER_01] Bio sam na jednom sutrtu u Skatsu

960
00:31:48,940 --> 00:31:52,200
[SPEAKER_01] kao Luka ne, Luke neme,

961
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo da uvod nasvi.

962
00:31:53,119 --> 00:31:54,200
[SPEAKER_01] Jednom su mene zvali

963
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:54,880
[SPEAKER_01] i ja se sjećam,

964
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] pater volenik me zvao.

965
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:58,700
[SPEAKER_01] I tada sam ja

966
00:31:58,700 --> 00:32:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] sa rukavicama o tome pričao.

967
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:03,059
[SPEAKER_01] Neko me otvoreno pitao o tome.

968
00:32:03,059 --> 00:32:04,640
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna studentica.

969
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pazi, ovo je bilo dvije treće.

970
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ona mene pita otvoreno javno.

971
00:32:09,460 --> 00:32:11,660
[SPEAKER_01] Šta vi mislite,

972
00:32:11,660 --> 00:32:12,359
[SPEAKER_01] don da mi rekao,

973
00:32:12,359 --> 00:32:14,559
[SPEAKER_01] jedan par želi živit zajedno,

974
00:32:14,559 --> 00:32:16,079
[SPEAKER_01] želi...

975
00:32:16,079 --> 00:32:17,859
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam bio tako nejasan.

976
00:32:18,660 --> 00:32:21,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam htio s jedne strane

977
00:32:21,140 --> 00:32:22,440
[SPEAKER_01] ići protiv crkve,

978
00:32:22,440 --> 00:32:24,759
[SPEAKER_01] ali nisam imao snage

979
00:32:24,759 --> 00:32:26,400
[SPEAKER_01] to braniti javno.

980
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:28,700
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nisi sam u sebi to...

981
00:32:28,700 --> 00:32:29,559
[SPEAKER_01] Jer nisam razumijel,

982
00:32:29,559 --> 00:32:30,779
[SPEAKER_01] nisam to prožvako dovoljno.

983
00:32:30,779 --> 00:32:32,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam imao hrabrost s nekom

984
00:32:32,380 --> 00:32:33,900
[SPEAKER_01] reći, ne smijete živit zajedno,

985
00:32:33,900 --> 00:32:34,900
[SPEAKER_01] nemojte to radit,

986
00:32:34,900 --> 00:32:35,319
[SPEAKER_01] to je zlo.

987
00:32:35,319 --> 00:32:35,940
[SPEAKER_01] A ona je rekao,

988
00:32:35,940 --> 00:32:37,059
[SPEAKER_01] pa dobro, najmjerno mi želimo,

989
00:32:37,059 --> 00:32:39,559
[SPEAKER_01] zar nije bolje prije nego poslije?

990
00:32:39,559 --> 00:32:41,099
[SPEAKER_00] Otkri da si ne pašemo prije nego poslije.

991
00:32:41,099 --> 00:32:42,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam prešutio nauk.

992
00:32:42,380 --> 00:32:43,839
[SPEAKER_01] Sad nisam govorio protiv crkve,

993
00:32:44,299 --> 00:32:44,980
[SPEAKER_01] ali sam prešutio.

994
00:32:44,980 --> 00:32:46,779
[SPEAKER_00] Nisi ga naglasio i objasnio.

995
00:32:46,779 --> 00:32:49,660
[SPEAKER_01] I tada jedna druga cura

996
00:32:49,660 --> 00:32:51,519
[SPEAKER_01] se digla i rekla,

997
00:32:51,519 --> 00:32:52,779
[SPEAKER_01] sram vas bilo.

998
00:32:52,779 --> 00:32:53,319
[SPEAKER_01] Pred svima.

999
00:32:53,319 --> 00:32:53,680
[SPEAKER_01] Tebi.

1000
00:32:53,680 --> 00:32:54,059
[SPEAKER_01] Meni.

1001
00:32:54,059 --> 00:32:55,920
[SPEAKER_01] Sram vas bilo.

1002
00:32:55,920 --> 00:32:56,420
[SPEAKER_01] Pred svima.

1003
00:32:56,420 --> 00:32:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] Nemoj se...

1004
00:32:58,460 --> 00:33:00,720
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to nisam nikad čula.

1005
00:33:00,720 --> 00:33:01,819
[SPEAKER_01] I ovo je ekskluziva.

1006
00:33:01,819 --> 00:33:03,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je ekskluziva.

1007
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:05,180
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je rekla,

1008
00:33:05,180 --> 00:33:06,720
[SPEAKER_01] kako vi kao svećenika,

1009
00:33:06,720 --> 00:33:07,839
[SPEAKER_01] katolički svećenik,

1010
00:33:07,839 --> 00:33:09,819
[SPEAKER_01] ovdje pred svim mladima,

1011
00:33:09,819 --> 00:33:12,759
[SPEAKER_01] ste prešutili nešto tako važno.

1012
00:33:12,759 --> 00:33:13,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ona vajda,

1013
00:33:13,500 --> 00:33:14,819
[SPEAKER_01] ja ne znam ko je to bilo.

1014
00:33:14,819 --> 00:33:16,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bih volio sad njoj se zahvaliti.

1015
00:33:16,779 --> 00:33:17,960
[SPEAKER_01] Što me prozvala.

1016
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:19,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ako pogleda će, znači da.

1017
00:33:19,619 --> 00:33:20,700
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, prozvala me.

1018
00:33:20,700 --> 00:33:22,940
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto sam govorio protiv šta.

1019
00:33:22,940 --> 00:33:24,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam prešutio.

1020
00:33:24,039 --> 00:33:25,240
[SPEAKER_01] Prešutio sam samo.

1021
00:33:25,240 --> 00:33:26,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si to, ono,

1022
00:33:26,920 --> 00:33:28,619
[SPEAKER_00] dao neki neutralni odgovor,

1023
00:33:28,619 --> 00:33:29,180
[SPEAKER_00] bez veze.

1024
00:33:29,180 --> 00:33:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] Sa rukavicama.

1025
00:33:29,880 --> 00:33:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] Samo da se ljudima svidim.

1026
00:33:31,559 --> 00:33:32,799
[SPEAKER_00] Samo da se svidim ljudima.

1027
00:33:32,799 --> 00:33:35,480
[SPEAKER_01] Mene hladan znoj oblio.

1028
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ona ti je rekla da kako možeš ti prešutiti

1029
00:33:39,500 --> 00:33:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] na katoličke crkve.

1030
00:33:40,579 --> 00:33:42,119
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto ne govorite jasno?

1031
00:33:42,119 --> 00:33:42,920
[SPEAKER_01] Istino, tako je.

1032
00:33:42,920 --> 00:33:45,339
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam i to jedna studentica.

1033
00:33:46,200 --> 00:33:47,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam išao doma.

1034
00:33:47,019 --> 00:33:48,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam pao u takvoj krizi.

1035
00:33:48,319 --> 00:33:51,059
[SPEAKER_01] Pomogu misliti.

1036
00:33:51,059 --> 00:33:53,359
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam nakon toga išao na studij i tako.

1037
00:33:53,359 --> 00:33:56,420
[SPEAKER_01] I to je brojilo u mene.

1038
00:33:56,420 --> 00:33:57,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se bacio u to.

1039
00:33:57,720 --> 00:34:00,700
[SPEAKER_01] E, kad je Don Damir se vratio 2007.

1040
00:34:00,700 --> 00:34:02,559
[SPEAKER_01] Više ne šuti.

1041
00:34:02,559 --> 00:34:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo sad do te teme.

1042
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:05,440
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

1043
00:34:06,660 --> 00:34:07,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je moje iskustvo.

1044
00:34:07,799 --> 00:34:13,920
[SPEAKER_01] Nitko ne ide iz neke zle volje to činiti.

1045
00:34:13,920 --> 00:34:15,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ta pač je namjerna jako dobra.

1046
00:34:15,820 --> 00:34:16,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ok?

1047
00:34:16,699 --> 00:34:17,679
[SPEAKER_01] I da se razumijem.

1048
00:34:17,679 --> 00:34:18,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ja to imam u moj rodbini.

1049
00:34:18,699 --> 00:34:20,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ja to vidim.

1050
00:34:20,199 --> 00:34:21,420
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, svi to radim.

1051
00:34:21,420 --> 00:34:22,940
[SPEAKER_01] Mnošto to čini.

1052
00:34:22,940 --> 00:34:24,300
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro namjerno.

1053
00:34:24,300 --> 00:34:24,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ok?

1054
00:34:24,659 --> 00:34:25,619
[SPEAKER_01] Uzmijemo da je dobro namjerno.

1055
00:34:25,619 --> 00:34:26,719
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, gdje je problem?

1056
00:34:27,900 --> 00:34:33,099
[SPEAKER_01] Problem je što djevojke ne razumiju kako mozak muški funkcionira.

1057
00:34:33,099 --> 00:34:35,739
[SPEAKER_01] Mi muškarci, mi smo kavaljeri.

1058
00:34:35,739 --> 00:34:36,940
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo lovci.

1059
00:34:36,940 --> 00:34:42,099
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki muškarac voli se u dvara djevojci i tako dalje.

1060
00:34:42,099 --> 00:34:42,699
[SPEAKER_01] I on lovi.

1061
00:34:42,699 --> 00:34:46,480
[SPEAKER_01] I ako on, ovo je na pocvestoj razini.

1062
00:34:46,480 --> 00:34:47,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam dugo oveme razmišljio.

1063
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:50,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ako on ulazi u neki brak.

1064
00:34:50,519 --> 00:34:53,039
[SPEAKER_01] I onda 5-6 mjeseci prije ide s njom živjeti.

1065
00:34:53,039 --> 00:34:53,739
[SPEAKER_01] I on je lovac.

1066
00:34:53,739 --> 00:34:55,980
[SPEAKER_01] Kakav će on biti u ti 5 mjeseci?

1067
00:34:55,980 --> 00:34:56,699
[SPEAKER_01] Naj, naj, naj.

1068
00:34:57,360 --> 00:34:58,119
[SPEAKER_01] Sve su prelative.

1069
00:34:58,119 --> 00:34:59,320
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

1070
00:34:59,320 --> 00:35:01,019
[SPEAKER_01] Jer zna da je na probi.

1071
00:35:01,019 --> 00:35:03,380
[SPEAKER_01] I ova se oduševi.

1072
00:35:03,380 --> 00:35:04,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ajme, meni.

1073
00:35:04,300 --> 00:35:06,119
[SPEAKER_01] On meni donose i doručak u krevet.

1074
00:35:06,119 --> 00:35:08,420
[SPEAKER_01] Pa on, on je tako uredan.

1075
00:35:08,420 --> 00:35:08,920
[SPEAKER_01] On je.

1076
00:35:08,920 --> 00:35:11,940
[SPEAKER_01] I zašto?

1077
00:35:11,940 --> 00:35:12,539
[SPEAKER_01] Jer on ju lovi.

1078
00:35:12,539 --> 00:35:14,059
[SPEAKER_01] I on zna da ona to očekuje.

1079
00:35:14,059 --> 00:35:17,139
[SPEAKER_01] I onda nakon 6 mjeseci oni ulaze u brak.

1080
00:35:17,139 --> 00:35:17,719
[SPEAKER_01] I on je ulovio.

1081
00:35:17,719 --> 00:35:18,400
[SPEAKER_01] Oženio se.

1082
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:19,159
[SPEAKER_01] I šta se dogodi?

1083
00:35:19,159 --> 00:35:20,920
[SPEAKER_01] On se upusti.

1084
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarnost.

1085
00:35:21,559 --> 00:35:22,159
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarnost.

1086
00:35:22,159 --> 00:35:22,860
[SPEAKER_01] E sada.

1087
00:35:22,860 --> 00:35:24,739
[SPEAKER_01] U čemu je problem?

1088
00:35:24,739 --> 00:35:26,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je stvarila

1089
00:35:26,820 --> 00:35:27,559
[SPEAKER_01] jednu sliku

1090
