[SPEAKER_01] najrealnija

1092
00:35:29,519 --> 00:35:31,380
[SPEAKER_01] i gradila sve na tome.

1093
00:35:31,380 --> 00:35:32,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ušla u brak

1094
00:35:32,840 --> 00:35:35,420
[SPEAKER_01] i videla da to ni baš nije tako.

1095
00:35:35,420 --> 00:35:36,139
[SPEAKER_01] On je se tamo

1096
00:35:36,139 --> 00:35:37,760
[SPEAKER_01] samo se tako predstavio.

1097
00:35:37,760 --> 00:35:39,199
[SPEAKER_01] On čak nije lagonamjerno.

1098
00:35:39,199 --> 00:35:40,280
[SPEAKER_01] Nego je muškarac bio.

1099
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:41,300
[SPEAKER_01] Tipičan muškarac.

1100
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:41,820
[SPEAKER_01] lovio je.

1101
00:35:41,820 --> 00:35:42,619
[SPEAKER_01] E sada.

1102
00:35:42,619 --> 00:35:43,239
[SPEAKER_01] Koji je razlika

1103
00:35:43,239 --> 00:35:43,980
[SPEAKER_01] ako nisu živjeli?

1104
00:35:43,980 --> 00:35:45,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ona ne bi imala tu pred sliku.

1105
00:35:45,739 --> 00:35:47,659
[SPEAKER_00] Odnosno tu uljepšanu sliku.

1106
00:35:47,659 --> 00:35:49,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ona bi ušla

1107
00:35:49,980 --> 00:35:51,059
[SPEAKER_01] bez ikakve slike.

1108
00:35:51,059 --> 00:35:52,099
[SPEAKER_01] Takve slike bar.

1109
00:35:52,099 --> 00:35:52,579
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

1110
00:35:52,579 --> 00:35:54,179
[SPEAKER_01] I ona bi ga prikvatila

1111
00:35:54,179 --> 00:35:55,380
[SPEAKER_01] u zdravlju i bolesti

1112
00:35:55,380 --> 00:35:56,239
[SPEAKER_01] u dobru i u zlu.

1113
00:35:56,239 --> 00:35:58,019
[SPEAKER_01] Prije braka

1114
00:35:58,019 --> 00:35:59,239
[SPEAKER_01] on se predstavljio

1115
00:35:59,239 --> 00:36:00,739
[SPEAKER_01] samo u dobru,

1116
00:36:00,739 --> 00:36:02,179
[SPEAKER_01] u najboljem

1117
00:36:02,179 --> 00:36:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] i onda ona opravdano pita

1118
00:36:04,739 --> 00:36:05,860
[SPEAKER_01] pa dobro šta je sad ovo?

1119
00:36:05,860 --> 00:36:07,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ok.

1120
00:36:07,119 --> 00:36:08,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se ugrađujem

1121
00:36:08,619 --> 00:36:09,679
[SPEAKER_01] oko moje teorije.

1122
00:36:09,679 --> 00:36:11,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam dugo o tome razmišljio

1123
00:36:11,960 --> 00:36:13,300
[SPEAKER_01] i to je zaključak

1124
00:36:13,300 --> 00:36:14,239
[SPEAKER_01] koji sam ja došao.

1125
00:36:14,239 --> 00:36:14,679
[SPEAKER_00] Razumijem.

1126
00:36:14,679 --> 00:36:16,840
[SPEAKER_00] Pojednostavio si jako

1127
00:36:16,840 --> 00:36:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] ali si nam sad rekao

1128
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:18,679
[SPEAKER_00] kako ti to vidiš.

1129
00:36:18,679 --> 00:36:20,119
[SPEAKER_01] Jer kako objasniti

1130
00:36:20,119 --> 00:36:22,260
[SPEAKER_01] da nakon kohapitacije

1131
00:36:22,260 --> 00:36:23,239
[SPEAKER_01] par godina

1132
00:36:23,239 --> 00:36:24,920
[SPEAKER_01] da baš ti paravi

1133
00:36:24,920 --> 00:36:25,719
[SPEAKER_01] završe

1134
00:36:25,719 --> 00:36:27,320
[SPEAKER_01] nakon nekoliko mjeseci

1135
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:28,199
[SPEAKER_01] što sam ja imao

1136
00:36:28,199 --> 00:36:29,599
[SPEAKER_01] u moje pastoralno iskustvo

1137
00:36:29,599 --> 00:36:30,219
[SPEAKER_01] i kao župnik

1138
00:36:30,219 --> 00:36:31,059
[SPEAKER_01] i kao studijski padan

1139
00:36:31,059 --> 00:36:32,699
[SPEAKER_01] sam to vidio u mojim očima.

1140
00:36:32,699 --> 00:36:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1141
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:35,159
[SPEAKER_01] I zato...

1142
00:36:35,159 --> 00:36:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je jedna razina.

1143
00:36:36,380 --> 00:36:36,559
[SPEAKER_00] Je.

1144
00:36:36,559 --> 00:36:37,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, razina toga da

1145
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:38,519
[SPEAKER_00] u stvari

1146
00:36:38,519 --> 00:36:41,260
[SPEAKER_00] onima koji žele

1147
00:36:41,260 --> 00:36:42,260
[SPEAKER_00] da im to pomogne

1148
00:36:42,260 --> 00:36:42,920
[SPEAKER_00] da bolje

1149
00:36:42,920 --> 00:36:44,320
[SPEAKER_00] da se pripreme

1150
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:45,260
[SPEAKER_00] u stvari za jedan

1151
00:36:45,260 --> 00:36:47,139
[SPEAKER_00] dugi, zajednički,

1152
00:36:47,139 --> 00:36:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] lijepi život.

1153
00:36:48,199 --> 00:36:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1154
00:36:48,440 --> 00:36:49,320
[SPEAKER_00] A druga stvar je

1155
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:50,380
[SPEAKER_00] nauk crkve.

1156
00:36:50,380 --> 00:36:51,840
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovo je iskustvo

1157
00:36:51,840 --> 00:36:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] zašto to plodova?

1158
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:54,619
[SPEAKER_00] A kako je?

1159
00:36:54,619 --> 00:36:55,719
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto crkva toliko?

1160
00:36:55,719 --> 00:36:57,860
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto u nauku crkve stoji

1161
00:36:57,860 --> 00:37:00,099
[SPEAKER_00] da ljudi ne žive zajedno

1162
00:37:00,099 --> 00:37:01,420
[SPEAKER_00] viđu da se trebaju...

1163
00:37:01,420 --> 00:37:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što se kaže u medijima

1164
00:37:02,619 --> 00:37:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] seks samo u braku.

1165
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:04,199
[SPEAKER_01] Je.

1166
00:37:04,199 --> 00:37:06,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bi ovdje jednu razliku radio

1167
00:37:06,099 --> 00:37:07,900
[SPEAKER_01] jer stvarno postoji

1168
00:37:07,900 --> 00:37:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] jedna razina gdje

1169
