[SPEAKER_01] gdje neko živi

1171
00:37:11,579 --> 00:37:12,519
[SPEAKER_01] ispod istog krova,

1172
00:37:12,519 --> 00:37:14,219
[SPEAKER_01] a žive kao brat i sestra,

1173
00:37:14,219 --> 00:37:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] ja to nikome ne preporučujem,

1174
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:20,980
[SPEAKER_01] ali ako ćemo gledati usko,

1175
00:37:20,980 --> 00:37:22,119
[SPEAKER_01] to nije grijeh,

1176
00:37:22,119 --> 00:37:22,900
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

1177
00:37:22,900 --> 00:37:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] da su odvojni,

1178
00:37:24,380 --> 00:37:25,539
[SPEAKER_01] evo,

1179
00:37:25,539 --> 00:37:26,519
[SPEAKER_01] zbog nekih financijskih,

1180
00:37:26,519 --> 00:37:27,500
[SPEAKER_01] ekonomskih razloga

1181
00:37:27,500 --> 00:37:28,139
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje.

1182
00:37:28,139 --> 00:37:30,019
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da,

1183
00:37:30,019 --> 00:37:31,880
[SPEAKER_01] jako je važno gledateljima

1184
00:37:31,880 --> 00:37:32,340
[SPEAKER_01] to znat,

1185
