1188
00:37:35,820 --> 00:37:37,480
[SPEAKER_01] čak možda rade javni sablas.

1189
00:37:37,480 --> 00:37:38,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nisam razumijela.

1190
00:37:38,199 --> 00:37:38,400
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

1191
00:37:38,400 --> 00:37:38,760
[SPEAKER_00] na primjer,

1192
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:39,400
[SPEAKER_00] imaš, aha,

1193
00:37:39,400 --> 00:37:40,860
[SPEAKER_00] imaš dečka i curu

1194
00:37:40,860 --> 00:37:42,059
[SPEAKER_00] koji žive u istom stanu,

1195
00:37:42,059 --> 00:37:43,260
[SPEAKER_00] ne žive zajedno,

1196
00:37:43,360 --> 00:37:44,559
[SPEAKER_00] nemaju seksualne odnose.

1197
00:37:44,559 --> 00:37:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ko brat i sestra.

1198
00:37:45,500 --> 00:37:46,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ko brat i sestra,

1199
